title: Eel Whole
description: Exotic unique eel with rich succulent flavor that is mildly sweet with a hint of earthiness. Excellent with roasted vegetables and mushrooms.

title: Wild Shad Roe
description: Seasonally sourced shad roe - classic American delicacy. Firm liver-like character with rich taste of spring. Sauté in butter onions and bacon.

title: Tuscan Branzino Whole
description: Citarella Exclusive! On your plate in less than 24 hours after leaving the water. Tender flaky mild sweet and juicy meat.

title: Arctic Char Whole
description: Native to icy northernmost waters of North America and Europe. Robust rich red to rosé pink fleshed fish. Iceland-sourced sustainably farmed. Perfect for smoking Scandinavian-style. Kosher-friendly.
